tags.name: Header
tags.query:
SELECT a.[BATCHID] AS [BatchID]
,a.[ITEM_CODE] AS [ItemCode]
,a.[ITEM_DESC] AS [ItemDescription]	
,a.[QTY]
,a.[DATE_CREATED] AS [CreationTS]
,b.[RecipeNumber]
,a.[CLASS_CODE] AS [ClassCode]
,a.[STATION_LOC] AS [StationID]
,a.[STATION] AS [StationName]
,a.[CREATE_TS] AS [RecordedTS]
,b.[RecipeID]
,b.[RecipeName]
,b.[RecipeDescription]
,b.[LineName]
,b.[MachineName]
,b.[ClientNumber]
,b.[RecordedTS]
FROM [BatchControl].[dbo].[tblBatches] a
INNER JOIN [BatchControl].[dbo].[tblRecipe] b
ON a.[ITEM_CODE] = b.RecipeName 
WHERE CAST(a.[BATCHID] AS NVARCHAR) LIKE '{[.]selectedBatchID}'

eventScripts.script:
if currentValue.value != previousValue.value and not(initialChange) :
		val = system.tag.readBlocking(["[.]secCount","[.]enCount","[.]setCount","[.]../DC_Triggers/TimerTrig"])
		secCount = val[0].value
		enCount = val[1].value
		setTimeSec = val[2].value
		manTrig = val[3].value
		if secCount < setTimeSec and enCount and manTrig:
			incVal = secCount+1
			system.tag.writeBlocking(["[.]secCount"], [incVal])
		if secCount >= setTimeSec and enCount and manTrig:
			system.tag.writeBlocking(["[.]secCount","[.]enCount"], [0,False])

if currentValue.value != previousValue.value and not(initialChange) :
		val = system.tag.readBlocking(["[.]secCount","[.]enCount","[.]setCount","[.]enTimer","[.]../LineFB/iBatchStateMachine"])

		manTrig = val[3].value

		if secCount >= setTimeSec and enCount and manTrig and batchState == 100:
